Cat Zodiac - An Astrological Guide to the Feline Mystique (2016).epub Gooner 

Publisher: Chronicle Books; 01 edition (1 Mar. 2016)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1452148287
ISBN-13: 978-1452148281

Even the most seasoned cat owner has found herself wondering why her cat meows for hours at the door to be let outside, only to turn around moments later and scratch at the door again to be let back in. Whether you're a brand-new cat owner, have lived with a feline companion or two for years, or are just intrigued by the astrological influences on the feline personality, this book is here to aid you in demystifying cat behaviors, using the stars as your guide.This zodiac collection delves into the inner lives of cats, exploring each sun sign and offering character traits, lifestyle insights, and relationship inclinations. Insightful, informative, and filled with whimsical illustrations, this book helps every cat owner unlock the secret of the feline mystique
